---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Il Brand — Luxe Noir</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Noise overlay -->
  <div class="noise"></div>

  <!-- Announcement bar -->
  <div class="announcement-bar">
    Spedizione gratuita sopra i &euro;150 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Reso facile entro 14 giorni
  </div>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="main-nav">
    <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce" class="nav-logo gradient-text">LUXE NOIR</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce#nuovi">Nuovi Arrivi</a>
      <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce#collezione">Donna</a>
      <a href="#">Uomo</a>
      <a href="#">Accessori</a>
      <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce/brand" class="active">Il Brand</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Cart icon -->
  <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce/carrello" class="cart-icon">
    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
      <path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"></path>
      <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line>
      <path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"></path>
    </svg>
    <span class="cart-badge">3</span>
  </a>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="brand-hero">
    <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">La Nostra Essenza</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Il <span class="gradient-text">Brand</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Dove l'artigianato incontra il design contemporaneo. Una storia di passione, materia e bellezza senza tempo.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Decorative line -->
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-inner">
      <div class="story-content">
        <p class="section-tag">La Nostra Storia</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Nato a <span class="gradient-text">Milano</span>, Fatto in <span class="gradient-text">Toscana</span></h2>
        <p class="story-text">Luxe Noir nasce nel 2019 nel cuore di Milano, dall'intuizione di Alessandra Neri: creare una maison che restituisca al lusso il suo significato pi&ugrave; autentico. Non ostentazione, ma sostanza. Non tendenza, ma permanenza.</p>
        <p class="story-text">Fin dal primo giorno, la filosofia &egrave; stata chiara: selezionare i migliori artigiani toscani, lavorare esclusivamente pellami e tessuti di prima scelta, e offrire un prodotto che resista al tempo &mdash; sia nella qualit&agrave; che nel design.</p>
        <p class="story-text">Ogni borsa, ogni accessorio &egrave; il risultato di oltre 40 ore di lavoro manuale. Non esistono scorciatoie quando si tratta di eccellenza. Questo &egrave; il nostro patto con chi ci sceglie.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-visual">
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-number">2019</div>
          <div class="visual-label">Anno di Fondazione</div>
        </div>
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-number">40+</div>
          <div class="visual-label">Ore per Ogni Pezzo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-number">100%</div>
          <div class="visual-label">Made in Italy</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-tag">La Nostra Promessa</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">I Nostri <span class="gradient-text">Valori</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c9a96e" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Artigianalit&agrave;</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Ogni prodotto &egrave; interamente realizzato a mano dai nostri maestri artigiani. Nessuna catena di montaggio, nessun compromesso. Solo mani esperte che trasformano la materia prima in arte da indossare.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c9a96e" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Sostenibilit&agrave;</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Utilizziamo esclusivamente pellami certificati provenienti da concerie toscane che rispettano i pi&ugrave; alti standard ambientali. Ogni scarto viene riutilizzato. Il packaging &egrave; realizzato in carta riciclata e inchiostri vegetali.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c9a96e" stroke-width="1.5">
            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Design Italiano</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Le nostre collezioni nascono dallo studio di forme essenziali e proporzioni equilibrate. Ogni linea &egrave; pensata per durare oltre le stagioni, con un'eleganza che non ha bisogno di gridare per farsi notare.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Workshop -->
  <section class="workshop-section">
    <div class="workshop-inner">
      <div class="workshop-image">
        <div class="workshop-placeholder">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(201,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="1">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Il Laboratorio</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="workshop-content">
        <p class="section-tag">Dove Nasce l'Eccellenza</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Il <span class="gradient-text">Laboratorio</span></h2>
        <p class="workshop-text">Il nostro laboratorio si trova sulle colline tra Firenze e Siena, in un edificio storico del XVIII secolo che un tempo ospitava una stamperia tessile. Le mura in pietra conservano il ricordo di secoli di artigianato.</p>
        <p class="workshop-text">Qui lavorano dodici maestri artigiani, alcuni dei quali con oltre trent'anni di esperienza nella pelletteria di alta gamma. Ogni fase della lavorazione &mdash; dal taglio alla cucitura, dalla tintura alla rifinitura &mdash; avviene sotto lo stesso tetto, garantendo un controllo di qualit&agrave; assoluto.</p>
        <p class="workshop-text">Ogni stagione apriamo le porte del laboratorio ai nostri clienti pi&ugrave; fedeli per giornate esclusive di visita, dove &egrave; possibile assistere alla creazione dei pezzi e personalizzare il proprio accessorio.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="founder-section">
    <div class="founder-inner">
      <div class="founder-content">
        <p class="section-tag">La Visionaria</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">La <span class="gradient-text">Fondatrice</span></h2>
        <h3 class="founder-name">Alessandra Neri</h3>
        <p class="founder-text">Nata a Milano nel 1987, Alessandra cresce tra i tessuti dell'atelier di sua nonna a Prato e le gallerie d'arte contemporanea di Brera. Dopo una laurea in Design al Politecnico di Milano e cinque anni come direttrice creativa in una delle pi&ugrave; importanti maison francesi, decide di tornare in Italia con un'idea precisa: dimostrare che il lusso autentico non ha bisogno di un logo visibile.</p>
        <p class="founder-text">Nel 2019 fonda Luxe Noir con un investimento personale e tre artigiani. Oggi il team conta dodici persone e i prodotti sono distribuiti in quattordici Paesi. Ogni pezzo porta ancora la sua supervisione diretta.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="founder-image">
        <div class="founder-placeholder">
          <div class="founder-avatar">AN</div>
          <span class="founder-caption">Alessandra Neri, Fondatrice</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="quote-section">
    <div class="quote-inner">
      <div class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
      <blockquote class="quote-text">
        Ogni pezzo racconta una storia.<br />
        La nostra sfida &egrave; far s&igrave; che sia anche la tua.
      </blockquote>
      <p class="quote-author">&mdash; Alessandra Neri</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Scopri la <span class="gradient-text">Collezione</span></h2>
      <p class="cta-desc">Esplora i nostri pezzi unici, pensati per chi cerca l'eccellenza senza compromessi.</p>
      <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce" class="btn-primary">Scopri la Collezione</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3 class="footer-logo gradient-text">LUXE NOIR</h3>
        <p class="footer-tagline">L'arte del lusso accessibile.</p>
        <p class="footer-address">Via Montenapoleone 42, 20121 Milano (MI)</p>
        <p class="footer-address">Tel. +39 02 7600 1234</p>
        <p class="footer-address">info@luxenoir.it</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Collezioni</h4>
        <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce#nuovi">Nuovi Arrivi</a>
        <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce#collezione">Donna</a>
        <a href="#">Uomo</a>
        <a href="#">Accessori</a>
        <a href="#">Capsule Collection</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Servizio Clienti</h4>
        <a href="#">Spedizioni</a>
        <a href="#">Reso gratuito</a>
        <a href="#">Pagamenti sicuri</a>
        <a href="#">Traccia il tuo ordine</a>
        <a href="#">Contattaci</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Seguici</h4>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#">Pinterest</a>
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#">TikTok</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Luxe Noir S.r.l. &mdash; P.IVA 12345678901 &mdash; Via Montenapoleone 42, Milano</p>
      <p class="footer-legal">
        <a href="#">Termini e Condizioni</a> &bull;
        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> &bull;
        <a href="#">Cookie Policy</a>
      </p>
      <p class="footer-demo">Demo template di Marco Munich</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

<style>
  /* ========== RESET & BASE ========== */
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #e8e0d4;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a0a0a; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #c9a96e; border-radius: 4px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #dbb878; }

  .noise {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.03;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-repeat: repeat;
  }
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e 0%, #f0d89c 40%, #c9a96e 60%, #a67c3d 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
  }

  /* ========== ANNOUNCEMENT BAR ========== */
  .announcement-bar {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 110;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d);
    color: #0a0a0a; text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 8px 16px;
  }

  /* ========== NAV ========== */
  .main-nav {
    position: fixed; top: 32px; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 105;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.75); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 3px;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.7); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.5px; transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: #c9a96e; }

  /* ========== CART ICON ========== */
  .cart-icon {
    position: fixed; top: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 100;
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2); border-radius: 50%;
    color: #c9a96e; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .cart-icon:hover { background: rgba(201,169,110,0.1); border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.5); }
  .cart-badge {
    position: absolute; top: -4px; right: -4px;
    width: 20px; height: 20px; background: #c9a96e; color: #0a0a0a;
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  /* ========== HERO ========== */
  .brand-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 160px 24px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-gradient {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1207 30%, #0a0a0a 50%, #12090a 70%, #0a0a0a 100%);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    animation: gradient 15s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes gradient {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 700px; }
  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a96e; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.7);
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .hero-line {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1px; height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #c9a96e, transparent);
  }

  /* ========== SECTION SHARED ========== */
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a96e; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ========== STORY ========== */
  .story-section {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 24px;
  }
  .story-inner {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .story-text {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .story-visual {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;
    padding-top: 60px;
  }
  .visual-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .visual-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.25); }
  .visual-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #c9a96e;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .visual-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.4);
  }

  /* ========== VALUES ========== */
  .values-section {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 100px;
  }
  .values-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px;
  }
  .value-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
    border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }
  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .value-icon {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(201,169,110,0.06);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .value-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .value-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.6);
  }

  /* ========== WORKSHOP ========== */
  .workshop-section {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 100px;
  }
  .workshop-inner {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .workshop-image {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
  }
  .workshop-placeholder {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #131313, #1a1a1a);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .workshop-placeholder span {
    font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(201,169,110,0.3);
  }
  .workshop-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* ========== FOUNDER ========== */
  .founder-section {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 100px;
  }
  .founder-inner {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr; gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .founder-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #c9a96e;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .founder-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(232,224,212,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .founder-image { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
  .founder-placeholder {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
  }
  .founder-avatar {
    width: 180px; height: 180px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,169,110,0.15), rgba(201,169,110,0.05));
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #c9a96e;
  }
  .founder-caption {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* ========== QUOTE ========== */
  .quote-section {
    padding: 80px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.06);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.06);
  }
  .quote-inner {
    max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;
  }
  .quote-mark {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 5rem; line-height: 1; color: rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
    margin-bottom: -20px;
  }
  .quote-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .quote-author {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: #c9a96e; letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  /* ========== CTA ========== */
  .cta-section {
    max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cta-desc {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300;
